QuoteSee is a stock and currency quote plasmoid for KDE.

FORMAT FOR SYMBOLS:
usdcad=x - USD to CAD
yhoo - Yahoo!

INSTALLATION PREREQUISITES (on Kubuntu)
cmake 
build-essential
kdelibs5-dev

QuoteSee was tested on Kubuntu 9.04 w/KDE4.3.2 and OpenSuSE 11.1 with Qt 4.5.2 and KDE 4.3.

Binary packages for Kubuntu, OpenSUSE, Mandriva and Arch are at:
http://www.kde-look.org/content/show.php/?content=101760